text: Charlie Fisher is an American football coach. He is the former wide receivers coach at Arizona State University, a position he had held since 2018. Fisher served as the head football coach at the University of West Georgia from 1993 to 1997 and Western Illinois University from 2016 to 2017. ==Head coaching record== ==References== ==External links== * Arizona State profile Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Arizona State Sun Devils football coaches Category:Eastern Kentucky Colonels football coaches Category:Lenoir–Rhyne Bears football coaches Category:Miami RedHawks football coaches Category:NC State Wolfpack football coaches Category:Ole Miss Rebels football coaches Category:Richmond Spiders football coaches Category:Temple Owls football coaches Category:Vanderbilt Commodores football coaches Category:West Georgia Wolves football coaches Category:Western Illinois Leathernecks football coaches Category:Eastern Kentucky University alumni Category:Springfield College (Massachusetts) alumni
